<F P=102>   BK3003084894 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 0500 GMT 30 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK3003084894 </F>
<F P=104>  Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 0500 GMT 30 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=105> Cambodian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] His Excellency [H.E.] Khieu Kanharit and H.E. Ung 
Teaseam, respectively state secretary and under state secretary 
for information, left Phnom Penh on the morning of 29 March for 
a three-day working visit to the Royal Kingdom of Thailand from 
29 to 31 March. In Thailand, their excellencies will lead a 
number of national and international reporters and TV crew, 
including those from National Radio of Cambodia, AKP, BBC of 
Great Britain, VOA, AFP, CAMBODIAN TIMES, ABC of Australia, 
PHNOM PENH POST, KYODO of Japan, INDOCHINA REPORT, LE MEKONG, 
and so on to visit an area bordering Cambodia in Surin Province 
of Thailand. They will hold a news conference there. 

</TEXT>

