                              the Network                   the Network                   the Network 

1. Light for   657.5          792.9          836.6          984.2          1,710          1,930 
daily life 

2. Industry    1,094.5        1,318.4        1,691.6        1,990.1        3,460          3,905 

3. Services    238.6          287.5          380.7          447.9          780            880 

4.             54.7           65.9           104.3          122.6          210            240 
