  [Text] Tokyo, March 31 -- French Foreign Minister Alain 
Juppe arrived at Narita Airport Thursday morning [31 March] for 
a four-day visit to Japan for talks with Japanese leaders. 
Juppe was invited by his Japanese counterpart Tsutomu Hata, 
