<F P=100> SOUTHEAST ASIA </F>
<F P=101> Burma </F>
<H3> <TI>   Finance Minister Attends Bangkok Conference </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Finance Minister Attends Bangkok Conference </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK3103162294 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1300 GMT 31 Mar 
94 </F>

<F P=103> BK3103162294 </F>
<F P=104>  Rangoon Radio Burma </F>
<F P=105>  Burmese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A Myanmar [Burmese] delegation led by Brigadier 
General Win Tin, finance and revenue minister, has departed 
Yangon [Rangoon] on a Thai Airways International flight for 
Bangkok. They will attend a conference on capital management in 
the Indochinese countries to be held in Bangkok, Thailand on 1 
April. 

</TEXT>

